00:13:12.770 --> 00:13:16.640 align:middle line:10%
>> Sunspots are one of the
most famous things that we talk

00:13:16.640 --> 00:13:19.960 align:middle line:10%
about with the sun,
discovered by Galileo.

00:13:19.960 --> 00:13:23.360 align:middle line:10%
