gets stretched

00:13:35.720 --> 00:13:38.900 align:middle line:84%
and it stores all
of this energy,

00:13:38.900 --> 00:13:41.930 align:middle line:90%
and it can only store so much.

00:13:41.930 --> 00:13:45.290 align:middle line:84%
