storing building up.

00:13:45.290 --> 00:13:47.810 align:middle line:84%
That impedes the
heat coming through

00:13:47.810 --> 00:13:51.080 align:middle line:84%
and that makes a
sunspot, this dark patch

00:13:51.080 --> 00:13:55.240 align:middle line:84%
