from that energy

00:14:07.980 --> 00:14:09.700 align:middle line:90%
but it comes back to the sun.

00:14:09.700 --> 00:14:13.040 align:middle line:84%
It looks like a beautiful
horseshoe-shaped filament

00:14:13.040 --> 00:14:14.480 align:middle line:90%
of gas.

00:14:14.480 --> 00:14:17.360 align:middle line:84%
A little more energy--
that prominence breaks,

00:14:17.360 --> 00:14:21.290 align:middle line:84%
