00:22:03.223 --> 00:22:04.890 align:middle line:84%
Not a doubt that I
wouldn't do it again.

00:22:04.890 --> 00:23:35.020 align:middle line:90%


00:23:35.020 --> 00:23:37.450 align:middle line:84%
>> It was a mystical
thing that had happened.

00:23:37.450 --> 00:23:40.570 align:middle line:84%
