it was like thousands, if not

00:23:40.570 --> 00:23:43.510 align:middle line:84%
millions of years ago when early
humans saw the first eclipse

00:23:43.510 --> 00:23:45.550 align:middle line:90%
and wondered what was going on.

00:23:45.550 --> 00:23:48.340 align:middle line:84%
>> Throughout time, various
cultures have recorded what

00:23:48.340 --> 00:23:50.950 align:middle line:84%
they thought was causing
a total solar eclipse.

00:23:50.950 --> 00:23:54.760 align:middle line:84%
>> A lot of the myths about
eclipses from ancient cultures

00:23:54.760 --> 00:23:57.760 align:middle line:84%
