00:24:08.770 --> 00:24:11.710 align:middle line:84%
>> The Vikings thought it was
a wolf that was eating the sun.

00:24:11.710 --> 00:24:13.480 align:middle line:84%
The indigenous
people of the north

00:24:13.480 --> 00:24:15.580 align:middle line:84%
tell stories of a
bear eating the sun.

00:24:15.580 --> 00:24:18.580 align:middle line:84%
