sun and casting a shadow.

00:24:21.630 --> 00:24:24.070 align:middle line:84%
Cultures thousands of
years ago were afraid.

00:24:24.070 --> 00:24:26.420 align:middle line:90%
They were afraid of this event.

00:24:26.420 --> 00:24:29.560 align:middle line:84%
>> If I was some indigenous
person living in the land

00:24:29.560 --> 00:24:31.060 align:middle line:84%
