00:24:31.060 --> 00:24:34.120 align:middle line:84%
I would have been
totally freaked out.

00:24:34.120 --> 00:24:35.950 align:middle line:84%
Instead, because I
knew it was happening,

00:24:35.950 --> 00:24:38.770 align:middle line:90%
I was in reverence of it all.

00:24:38.770 --> 00:24:41.570 align:middle line:84%
>> If you understand
how things work,

00:24:41.570 --> 00:24:43.460 align:middle line:84%
then you're no longer
afraid of them.

00:24:43.460 --> 00:24:46.150 align:middle line:84%
>> There have been some great
examples when one particular

00:24:46.150 --> 00:24:48.850 align:middle line:84%
culture or person's
understanding of science

00:24:48.850 --> 00:24:52.840 align:middle line:84%
or nature around them has given
