00:26:05.330 --> 00:26:08.830 align:middle line:84%
and they timed a lot
of the cultural rituals

00:26:08.830 --> 00:26:10.690 align:middle line:90%
around these moments.

00:26:10.690 --> 00:26:14.140 align:middle line:84%
And that allowed
the priests to use

00:26:14.140 --> 00:26:16.660 align:middle line:84%
that moment and that
knowledge to give them

00:26:16.660 --> 00:26:19.390 align:middle line:84%
an advantage over
everybody else.

00:26:19.390 --> 00:26:22.240 align:middle line:84%
>> All too often science
