00:27:02.740 --> 00:27:04.300 align:middle line:90%
I think.

00:27:04.300 --> 00:27:07.940 align:middle line:84%
Science literacy is very
important for a society.

00:27:07.940 --> 00:27:09.880 align:middle line:84%
>> And if we can be
