00:28:52.425 --> 00:28:53.225 align:middle line:90%
in nature.

00:28:53.225 --> 00:28:57.170 align:middle line:90%


00:28:57.170 --> 00:29:02.270 align:middle line:84%
This is a critical difference
between philosophy and physics.

00:29:02.270 --> 00:29:06.400 align:middle line:84%
