personal opinion or bias

00:29:06.400 --> 00:29:08.370 align:middle line:90%
to be part of your answer.

00:29:08.370 --> 00:29:11.830 align:middle line:10%
And that is something that
science simply cannot allow.

00:29:11.830 --> 00:29:14.410 align:middle line:84%
Bias and personal
opinion can push you

00:29:14.410 --> 00:29:16.870 align:middle line:84%
in the wrong
direction, or worse,

00:29:16.870 --> 00:29:22.330 align:middle line:84%
force you to force your data
to support the theory you want

00:29:22.330 --> 00:29:26.110 align:middle line:84%
instead of allowing the data
to guide you towards the more

00:29:26.110 --> 00:29:27.580 align:middle line:90%
correct theory.

00:29:27.580 --> 00:29:30.270 align:middle line:10%
>> Science is all
about a process.

00:29:30.270 --> 00:29:32.530 align:middle line:10%
It starts when you
observe a phenomenon

00:29:32.530 --> 00:29:34.420 align:middle line:10%
that you don't understand.

00:29:34.420 --> 00:29:37.390 align:middle line:84%
And observing something
you don't understand always

00:29:37.390 --> 00:29:39.040 align:middle line:90%
leads you to ask questions.

00:29:39.040 --> 00:29:43.180 align:middle line:84%
