00:31:12.550 --> 00:31:14.980 align:middle line:84%
around you, because if
you observe, then maybe

00:31:14.980 --> 00:31:16.570 align:middle line:90%
you will wonder.

00:31:16.570 --> 00:31:19.570 align:middle line:84%
And then if you have wonder,
you'll ask questions,

00:31:19.570 --> 00:31:24.340 align:middle line:84%
and those will lead you
to research and to really

00:31:24.340 --> 00:31:25.780 align:middle line:90%
do good science.

00:31:25.780 --> 00:31:28.840 align:middle line:84%
>> I think if anything were
to inspire a person about

00:31:28.840 --> 00:31:31.780 align:middle line:84%
the scientific realm, I
think this would do it.

00:31:31.780 --> 00:31:35.920 align:middle line:84%
>> Knowing why it works
